name: COPE Minute Survey
description: Survey includes information regarding a participant’s COVID-19 vaccination experience.

name: COVID-19 Participant Experience (COPE)
description: Survey includes information about the impact of COVID-19 on participant mental and physical health.

name: Overall Health
description: Survey includes information about how participants report levels of individual health.

name: Lifestyle
description: Survey includes information on participant smoking, alcohol and recreational drug use.

name: The Basics
description: This survey includes participant demographic information.

name: Personal and Family Health History
description: Survey includes information about the medical history of a participant and their immediate family members.

name: Social Determinants of Health
description: Survey includes information about the social determinants of health, including a participant’s neighborhood, social life, stress, and feelings about everyday life.

name: Health Care Access & Utilization
description: Survey includes information about a participant’s access to and use of health care.
